{
  "text": "In this paper, we show that Modified SP iterative method converges to the fixed point of contraction mappings (3). Also, we establish an equivalence between convergence of iterative methods (1) and [CITATION_1] . For the sake of completness, we give a comparison result between the rate of convergences of iterative methods (1) and [CITATION_2] , and it thus will be shown that Picard-S iteration method is still the fastest method. Finally, a data dependence result for the fixed point of the contraction mappings (3) is proven.",
